description:

Our new EP - $10
Our new T Shirt - $20
A Signed Poster - $5

And we'll also throw in

A large sticker
A Phat Wristband
AND 2 Custom Guitar Picks
(Items only available at shows otherwise)

On top for FREE! Saving $10! Grab one before they sell out! xx.

(If you are ordering from Interstate/International/Rural NSW, please select the "ADD INTERSTATE/INTERNATIONAL POSTAGE" with your relevant T Size option)

name: "Steps Worth Taking" New EP! Hard Copy + Digital Copy!
description:
It's here, it's here! The brand new EP from "Kiss Me!" 
"Steps Worth Taking" is all about moving onwards and upwards with your life. There are songs about the hardships in life in regards to friendship and love.. About escaping, feeling young and free.. What it's like to always be friendzoned and a good old "F*ck You!" to anyone who has ever doubted you!

You have the option to select whether you would like us to sign your CD (at no additional cost) or to leave it blank xx.

(If ordering Interstate/International/Rural NSW, please select "ADD INTERSTATE/INTERNATIONAL POSTAGE" and relevant T Size Option)

name: Zombie Apocalypse Black Tee! -Presale-
description:
The Zombie Apocalypse is here but never fear because we here at "Kiss Me!" will serve and defend our fans! Well Chaff and Jesse will, Ian seems to not realize what's going on..

Check out this brand new T Shirt design featuring a zombie cat! All shirts are in the same style (Unisex. No gender differentiation).

(If ordering Interstate/International/Rural NSW, please select "ADD INTERSTATE/INTERNATIONAL POSTAGE" and relevant T Size Option)

name: Tour Presale Tickets!
description:
Get your tickets to the "Hey! This Looks Awfully Familiar!" East Coast & New Zealand Tour 2013.

Buy now and print your ticket off to save time and also guarantee entry to these events!

Please select the venue* (in your relevant state) you wish to attend!


*You must present your ID/receipt upon arrival to the venue for entry. 
**Note. This used to be the Romantic Lunch With Chaff. This option is still available.. because you know you love him ;D xx.

name: Donations (They really help)
description:
So you love the band, the songs and have the merch but you still want to do more? This is where we can help you, help us :D

Check out the selection of donation options in the drop down menu. Every donation goes towards using the money for recording, new merch, touring and anything else that requires cash.

It's you guys who make the difference to us. We feel so blessed that people care about our band and want to help us. 

So much love <3 xx.
